          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "/by Authors/ At energies beyond the threshold for",
                "populating excited analog states, coincidence",
                "measurements with adequate neutron energy resolution",
                "should yield cross sections smaller than the",
                "noncoincidence- p' (the analog state) spectra. In",
                "addition, the neutron spectra gated by p' events should",
                "peaks corresponding to excited analog states as well as",
                "the ground state.",
                "/by Authors/ The inconsistencies between (p,n) and",
                " (p,np') measurements was observed for Bi-209 target",
                "but not for Ta-181 and Au-197 targets. p'-analog state."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
